criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients who had been hospitalized in an acute care hospital for two or more days
             within the past 90 days;

          -  residents of a nursing home or long-term care facility;

          -  recipients of recent intravenous antibiotic therapy, chemotherapy or wound care within
             the past 30 days;

          -  or patients who attended a hospital or hemodialysis clinic.

        Exclusion Criteria:
